    "description": {
        "en-US": "<b> * Breaking News: * </b>\n<ul><li>   <b> New version 1.3.7 </b> full compatible with Thunderbird 31 and later.</li><li>   Configurable <b>Action for Window Close Button / ALT+F4 </b>, including recommended setting <b>\"Close Current Tab\"</b>! (like Hide C. Titlebar Plus for Firefox)</li><li>   Configurable <b>\"Thunderbird\" application-main-button</b> at top-left corner!, like Firefox's one.</li></ul>\nFinally, the Thunderbird version of Firefox's \"Hide Caption Titlebar Plus\" addon. Starting with a lite version for Windows.\n\nTo \"Maximize your screen content space\", plus Tabs-on-top in Windows Aero Basic (non glass) desktops (like Thunderbird does in Aero Glass).\n(Having Tabs at screen's top-edge make them easier to click, especially if you have several of them)\n\n\nTip for more space:  You can right-click -&gt; uncheck the Menu-bar to make it auto hide. (It'll show by pressing ALT)\n\n\nThis addon was tested on Win7-64 with Aero Basic and Aero-Glass and also in WinXP. \nYou are very welcome to report any bugs/issues at Support-site link. Please don't report them in the Reviews here.\n\nEnjoy!"
    },
